text:
LC volleyball at No. 3 in Class 1A rankings 
The Bellingham Herald Order Reprint of this Story 
The Lynden Christian volleyball team (7-2) is ranked at No. 3 in Class 1A of the recent Washington State Coaches Association poll. 
No other Whatcom County team is ranked but Burlington-Edison (8-0) is No. 1 in Class 2A and Anacortes (5-3) is at No. 10. Related content
